**Original author :** Blatti Yves

Catalog install overwrites the iFrame size parameters of component.

in catalog @script.php@ :

```

        // set default params
        $params = array('iframewidth'=>400,'iframeheight'=>600);
        $this->setParams($params);
```


we need to test if values exists before overwrite them.

**Fixed versions :** 4.3.2
